{"tid":2321781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭購科興疫苗　學者指　抗體水平低　不良反應比例高　疼痛噁心","createTime":"2020-12-11T19:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T01:49:02.000Z","uid":261647,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9324a4d84c65f824ea5f1b8d693bde3a9d25cd","tid":2321781,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T19:33:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/3786091131430592/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.907682852604782%2F3786091131430592%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=2c2f17bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/3786091131430592/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：前線科技人員<br />\n<br />\n國產科興 Sinovac 武肺疫苗雖然未發表第三階段測試結果，但在十一月頭發表第二階段測試時，Thomas Campbell (associate dean for clinical research at the University of Colorado) 及牛津大學學者 Eyck Freymann 分析有關數據後分別表示：<br />\n<br />\n- 該疫苗在人體血管內產生的抗體水平要 #低於新冠病毒康復者。相比之下，美國製藥公司Moderna和輝瑞的疫苗產生的抗體水平，與新冠病毒康復者的抗體水平相當，甚至是更高。<br />\n<br />\n- 743名參與者中的一部分 #出現了不良反應，這個比例在有的試驗組高達38%。這表示該滅活疫苗 #毒性更大，意味著人們更有可能經歷副作用，比如 #疼痛 、#噁心 等嚴重的反應。<br />\n<br />\n當然，這些評論只是外國勢力意圖打擊我國的惡意評論，最終只會拿石頭砸自己的腳，所有愛國愛港的市民將一貫堅持「信政府，唔怕！」的精神去爭打疫苗，並由高官帶頭做起。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-vaccine-covid-diplomacy-/5671393.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fchina-vaccine-covid-diplomacy-%2F5671393.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=d7c709fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/china-vaccine-covid-diplomacy-/5671393.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/coronavirus-vaccine-china-trial-sinovac/2020/11/18/4e47b0fe-294f-11eb-9c21-3cc501d0981f_story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fasia_pacific%2Fcoronavirus-vaccine-china-trial-sinovac%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2F4e47b0fe-294f-11eb-9c21-3cc501d0981f_story.html&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=90b1b84c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/coronavirus-vaccine-china-trial-sinovac/2020/11/18/4e47b0fe-294f-11eb-9c21-3cc501d0981f_story.html</a><br />\n<br />\n更詳細資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/3785762358130136/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.907682852604782%2F3785762358130136%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=2b206f3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/3785762358130136/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZos6mb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZos6mb.jpg&h=0fe3dd52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7501619bec3de07164a895dcaeadeaffae10cef","tid":2321781,"uid":383914,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T19:40:15.000Z","msg":"問責官員打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我哋市民先有信心架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d311764a8c5386df4ceb66c46cfafc77f9284cf8","tid":2321781,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:31:53.000Z","msg":"所以咪要多啲支那廢老同藍屍試囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11eba6e8419c49bd552862fe68ffb98b549420c1","tid":2321781,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKVfx1d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKVfx1d.gif&h=e8c94c37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1373f8748